{"tid":899383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪個個人屋企都日嘈夜嘈？","createTime":"2018-11-12T11:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T12:36:01.000Z","uid":57649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a31205eb839b9b17ef6c794acf0e197987005c3f","tid":899383,"uid":57649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"由唔知幾時開始屋企人一聚埋會嘈交 <br />\n<br />\n細個日日都只係可以自己匿埋喺廁所喊 驚佢地一見我喊就搵嘢嚟嘈<br />\n<br />\n到大個開始懂更加對呢個情況束手無策 咩都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n點解一家人唔可以互相體諒下 一人少句 唔好搞到每次都不歡而散<br />\n<br />\n我只係有一個小小願望 就係有日可以一家人齊齊整整、開開心心咁食餐飯<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都分享下自己故事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fceb5aa8f9b17f39fbd92e6b2f26891a2ffd98dc","tid":899383,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"已經變咗冷戰好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffad0ece91de7f7ff544b9ce02fcb32545e15ec","tid":899383,"uid":57649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fceb5aa8f9b17f39fbd92e6b2f26891a2ffd98dc","tid":899383,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"已經變咗冷戰好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:47:47.000Z","msg":"對住唔識既人就大方到 但偏偏對屋企人就咁小器<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80740c9b26722e66040f042e7e156f0c59c2c16","tid":899383,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:58:58.000Z","msg":"屋企都冇點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37393ab48c1a70c473dab529138dc7ddaedfdd54","tid":899383,"uid":196440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"嘈到而家屋企得返自己一個住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}